        <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
        <description>A .NET library for screen recording in Windows, using Microsoft Media Foundation for realtime encoding to h264 video or PNG images.</description>
        <summary />
        <releaseNotes>- Fixed bug that prevented reusing of Recorder instance.
- Fixed issue with variable framerate and recording of desktop where no changes occur for some time.
- Fixed audio glitches when mouse cursor rapidly changes.
- Fixed audio resampling for mono input.
- Fixed crash if disposing Recorder instance while recording was in progress.
- Fixed crash if recording with audio input enabled but no audio devices exist.</releaseNotes>
